{"tid":1420690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如改名連登發佈會","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:45:30.000Z","uid":276020,"like":1,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1935ad7a9734f2aba1a4bf0cfbe89e6762e79a74","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"我想講，不如將［民間記者會］，改名為［<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登發佈會</span></span>］<br />\n<br />\n1. 雖然講咗話只係一部分人嘅意見，但係用連登正名，係連登一部份人嘅意見好似會更好。<br />\n<br />\n2.用發佈會感覺會比較好，始終記者嘅提問好勁，如果回答記者提問，感覺好容易中伏，會講錯野。我哋嘅目標都係表達我地做緊d咩，做依d野有咩目的。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇大台不談判不妥協</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果政府回應發佈會嘅野，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔可以回應！！</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以將發佈會變成同政府溝通嘅渠道</span></span>，我哋只係同記者，同大眾市民溝通。"},{"pid":"a6cac996bc6d6cca7f9beb677ec9fe15edce97fa","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c35da56f738aa809f852052afe7185807e1b8b76","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"477f784bcba84b0116634021d8d1a32ee7f91beb","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e250bcf2ca46015eaf5b9d98316a71557c740b71","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d3c728b2685fb7a7ddce777d3010a81dd89ec4cc","tid":1420690,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1a82c4263afc031ad7cd124a11359b616b4ee91b","tid":1420690,"uid":261433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"Agree 最後一段。"},{"pid":"098343d02